pdesc: Yumify is a front-end web application built using React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. It features pages for Home, Menu, About Us, and Book a Table functionalities. Users can navigate through these pages seamlessly to explore the restaurant's offerings and reserve a table.

The Dice Game is a luck-based web app created with React, JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. Players select a face of the giant dice, aiming to match it for a win. The game records the number of turns, rewarding higher scores for fewer turns.

The To-Do List Web App, developed with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, simplifies task management. Users can effortlessly add and delete tasks, ensuring efficient organization without the completion feature.
The Calculator Web App, designed with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, offers basic arithmetic functions. With intuitive controls, users can perform calculations efficiently on various devices.
